data.description: $5000 BUYER INCENTIVE! Sellers concession maybe be used for any buyers fee, costs, charge or expenditure to the extent allowed by lender & will be paid upon successful closing for full price offer. Discover this classic 1950 Ranch-style gem in the heart of Tempe. Offering 3 bedrooms, 1 bath, 1,368 sq ft of living space, this home is perfectly situated just minutes away from ASU, downtown Tempe, SCNM. With easy access to Loop 101, 202 & 60 freeways, commuting is a breeze. Inside, you'll find an updated kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances that come with the home, elegant quartz countertops, a stylish subway-tiled backsplash, and tile wood plank flooring.
